reviewText: This DVD is a Short Version of what You will find on the Longer versions (15 Minutes,as opposed to 145+),but the cream of the Intermissions has been skimmed to bring You only the best ones! Including some that has not been seen in 40+ Years!
Classic Intermissions, poor quality, I've bought better quality of the same clips elsewhere.  They do include alot of clips but just not up to my standards.
